\f0\fs24 \cf0 8 - Accept your fate\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1 \cf0 \expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
The Stoics believed in accepting fate, but that didn\'92t mean falling victim to it. When something bad happened to you, they believed you could turn it into both an opportunity to improve your character and take a new direction. Look at a challenge that you have faced or are now facing. How can it serve your quest for a more virtuous life?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f2\b \cf0 Stomach pain.
\f1\b0 \
\'d7 Opportunity to be more selective in the quality of food and appreciate them at reduced portions.\
\'d7 Pivot to a more appreciative of the opportunity of good health, and to not be a victim but to change my ways in response to my body, through restraint and discipline with attention & discernment. Prove that despite adversity I won\'92t be a spoilsport. Choose to practise what I preach regarding using positivity to overcome.
